---
title: Chorizo and Black Bean Chilli with Tortilla Chips, Soured Cream and Cheese
description: Our Chorizo and Black Bean Chilli makes the best of beans. Flavoured with chipotle for a rich, smoky and fruity flavour with a kick from the chipotle chillies, it's the chilli you didn't know you needed.
